            "text": "4632 - وَ رَوَى إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ عَمَّارٍ قَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:45:16",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/45/16",
      "text": [
        ": قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ أَ يَنْظُرُ اَلْمَمْلُوكُ إِلَى شَعْرِ مَوْلاَتِهِ قَالَ \"نَعَمْ وَ إِلَى سَاقِهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4632 - Ishaq ibn Ammar narrated that he said to Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as): \"Can a servant look at the hair of his mistress?\"\nThe Imam replied: \"Yes, and at her legs as well.\""
        ]
      }
